{
  "stem": "1641.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Then-- then you can see the girls lying around where the blood was trickling down their legs.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "They're with periods, obviously.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And later on you could find the girls who had-- who had no periods, who just couldn't walk fast enough, who couldn't go as fast as the BMW motorbike, is a certain speed, even at the lowest level, it's going, you know.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And so the women were-- usually there was a brain in the snow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And after the brain was the woman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "Brain, woman.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "It was where the brain flew out, two meters to the left, and then the woman was lying next to it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And then as we went on, all night we marched.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "I remember seeing thousands upon thousands of mostly women, but there were men too, of course.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "It was the first night we marched right through.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And the next day we marched right through.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And of course people used up all their food by then, with no more food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "But we could eat a bit of snow now and then.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And then we arrived the night of the second night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "We arrived to a kind of a farm.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And there was a building where it was usually-- would housed the cows, a building which had a lot of straw in it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And I was lucky enough to get into the building.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And I climbed up on a-- on a-- a few-- a step ladder.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And there was a-- it was a building for pigs and cows.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "I don't know what the English word for it is for such a building.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "Anyhow, I was lying in the straw, and just stretching out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And another big group of Polish Jewish people came.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And they took over the building.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And they talked Yiddish to each other.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
